</div>
<div class="card-grid">
<div class="card" style="border-color:#0060FF"><h3 style="color:#4488FF">Unreal Engine 5</h3><p>Nanite virtualized geometry, Lumen GI, Chaos physics. Industry standard for virtual production, games, and architectural visualization.</p></div>
<div class="card" style="border-color:#00E5FF"><h3 style="color:#00E5FF">Unity HDRP</h3><p>High Definition Render Pipeline. Deferred rendering, volumetric fog, TAA. Excellent multi-platform targeting. C# scripting with Burst compiler.</p></div>
<div class="card" style="border-color:#00FF41"><h3 style="color:#00FF41">Godot 4</h3><p>Open source. Vulkan backend, Global Illumination via SDFGI and Voxel GI. GDScript + C# + C++. Lightweight, no licensing fees.</p></div>
<div class="card" style="border-color:#FF6D00"><h3 style="color:#FF9240">TouchDesigner</h3><p>Real-time node-based. GLSL shaders, TOP/SOP pipelines, Vulkan backend (TD2023+). The live performance and installation standard.</p></div>
</div>
