<!-- SECTION 7: PROCEDURAL RENDERING -->
<section class="hidden" id="procedural">
<h2>// Procedural Rendering</h2>
<p>Procedural techniques generate content algorithmically rather than storing it explicitly. Noise-based terrain, signed distance fields for geometry, procedural textures, and L-system vegetation reduce storage requirements while enabling infinite variation.</p>
